<item>
            <title>[LU-12951] LL_IOC_GETOBDCOUNT return wrong MDT counts</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12951</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We used llapi_get_obd_count() to get MDT/OST counts, which call LL_IOC_GETOBDCOUNT&lt;br/&gt;
internally.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;However, we return lmv-&amp;gt;lmv_mdt_descs.ltd_tgts_size as MDT count, this is not right.&lt;br/&gt;
@ltd_tgts_size could be larger than actual MDT count,  as we preallocate ltd_tgts and resize it if necessary.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
